\color black
With the image illumation normalized, the watershed transform can be used
 to segment out the brighter regions of the image which will be the dune
 sunny sides.
 The watershed implementation used is provided by the OpenCV library, and
 is a variant of the implementation proposed in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
